src_text: Perry stated that he would "return to Texas to assess the results of tonight's caucus, determine whether there is a path forward for myself in this race", but later said that he would remain in the race and compete in the January 21 South Carolina primary.

src_text: They can see very well in the dark with night vision, and move very stealthily, too. Ocelots hunt their prey by blending in with their surroundings then pouncing on their prey.
ref_text: Gaueko ikusmena dutenez, oso ongi ikusten dute gauez eta isil-isilik mugitzeko gai dira, gainera. Ozeloteak ingurunean ezkutatu eta harrapakinak ustekabean harrapatzen dituzte haien gainera salto eginda.
hyp_text: Etxeak oso ondo ikusten dute ilunabarrean begi-nola ikusten dute, eta, gainera, oso eremu txiki eramaten dira. Ocelotek harrapakin egiten dute inguruko beraiarekin nahastuta, eta, gero, harrapakin hartzen dute.

src_text: When a small group of living things (a small population) gets separated from the main population that they came from (like if they move over a mountain range or a river, or if they move to a new island so that they can't easily move back) they will often find themselves in a different environment than they were in before.
ref_text: Izaki bizidunen talde txiki bat (populazio txiki bat) jatorrizko populazio nagusitik bereizten denean (adibidez, mendikate edo ibai batetik mugituz gero, edo uharte berri batetik erraz itzuli ezin izanez gero), lehen ez bezalako ingurune batean aurkituko da sarritan.
hyp_text: Batzuk populazio txiki bat (bizidun batzuk) banantzen da, jatorrizko populazioaren parte zena (adibidez, mendi-tartean edo ibaian igarotzen da, edo uharte berri batean joaten da ez dauden itzaltzen), eta beren berreskuratzeko ez dute aukera, beren inguruan beste lekuan aurkituko dira, aurrekoarekin aldaerik handi bat izango baita.

src_text: Technological determinism is a term that encompasses a wide range of ideas in practice, from technology-push or the technological imperative to a strict sense that human destiny is driven by an underlying logic associated with scientific laws and their manifestation in technology.

hyp_text: Ezagutzen da, zuzendariak hasi direnean, bi jokabideak agertzen dira bere aurreko nagusiak zuzentzen hasi direnean. Espektrogramaren amaieran dagoen alde bat, “gizonen artean” (edo emakumeen artean) irauten saiatzen da.

src_text: Appropriate use of blogs "can empower students to become more analytical and critical; through actively responding to Internet materials, students can define their positions in the context of others' writings as well as outline their own perspectives on particular issues (Oravec, 2002).
